{"meta":{"title":"Ether 5","canonicalUrl":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/5?lang=eng","contentType":"text/html","audio":[{"mediaUrl":"https://media2.ldscdn.org/assets/scriptures/the-book-of-mormon-another-testament-of-jesus-christ/2015-11-2190-ether-05-female-voice-64k-eng.mp3","voice":{"name":"female"}},{"mediaUrl":"https://media2.ldscdn.org/assets/scriptures/the-book-of-mormon-another-testament-of-jesus-christ/2015-11-2190-ether-05-male-voice-64k-eng.mp3","voice":{"name":"male"}}],"pageAttributes":{"data-asset-id":"69a22f86a6a5b77416e0cc0aecc60bdc2250a7c5","data-aid":"128354524","data-aid-version":"5","data-content-type":"chapter","data-uri":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/5","lang":"eng","data-orig-id":"69a22f86a6a5b77416e0cc0aecc60bdc2250a7c5","xmlns:xsi":"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance"}},"content":{"head":{"page-meta-social":{"pageMeta":{"title":"Ether 5","description":"Three witnesses and the work itself will stand as a testimony of the truthfulness of the Book of Mormon."},"pageSocial":{"title":"Ether 5","description":"Three witnesses and the work itself will stand as a testimony of the truthfulness of the Book of Mormon."}},"links":[{"type":"array","rel":"stylesheet","orig-type":"text/css","href":"css/style_classic-scripture.css"}],"scripts":[]},"body":"<header>\n<p class=\"title-number\" data-aid=\"128354546\" id=\"title_number1\">Chapter 5</p>\n<p class=\"study-summary\" data-aid=\"128354548\" id=\"study_summary1\">Three witnesses and the work itself will stand as a testimony of the truthfulness of the Book of Mormon.</p>\n</header>\n<div class=\"body-block\">\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"128354550\" id=\"p1\"><span class=\"verse-number\">1 </span>And now I, Moroni, have written the words which were commanded me, according to my memory; and I have told you the things which I have <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note1a\"><sup class=\"marker\">a</sup>sealed</a> up; therefore touch them not in order that ye may translate; for that thing is forbidden you, except by and by it shall be wisdom in God.</p>\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"128354551\" id=\"p2\"><span class=\"verse-number\">2 </span>And behold, ye may be privileged that ye may show the plates unto <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note2a\"><sup class=\"marker\">a</sup>those</a> who shall assist to bring forth this work;</p>\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"128354553\" id=\"p3\"><span class=\"verse-number\">3 </span>And unto <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note3a\"><sup class=\"marker\">a</sup>three</a> shall they be shown by the power of God; wherefore they shall <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note3b\"><sup class=\"marker\">b</sup>know</a> of a surety that these things are <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note3c\"><sup class=\"marker\">c</sup>true</a>.</p>\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"128354555\" id=\"p4\"><span class=\"verse-number\">4 </span>And in the mouth of three <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note4a\"><sup class=\"marker\">a</sup>witnesses</a> shall these things be established; and the <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note4b\"><sup class=\"marker\">b</sup>testimony</a> of three, and this work, in the which shall be shown forth the power of God and also his word, of which the Father, and the Son, and the Holy Ghost bear record—and all this shall stand as a testimony against the world at the last day.</p>\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"128354556\" id=\"p5\"><span class=\"verse-number\">5 </span>And if it so be that they repent and <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note5a\"><sup class=\"marker\">a</sup>come</a> unto the Father in the name of Jesus, they shall be received into the kingdom of God.</p>\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"128354558\" id=\"p6\"><span class=\"verse-number\">6 </span>And now, if I have no authority for these things, judge ye; for ye shall know that I have authority when ye shall see me, and we shall stand before God at the last day. Amen.</p>\n</div>\n<footer class=\"study-notes\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"chapter\">\n<li data-marker=\"5\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"verse\">\n<li data-marker=\"1\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note1a\" data-full-marker=\"1a\">\n<p data-aid=\"128354560\" id=\"note1a_p1\"><span data-note-category=\"cross-ref\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/27.7-11,21?lang=eng#p8\">2 Ne. 27:8 (7–11, 21)</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/ether/4.4-7?lang=eng#p5\">Ether 4:5 (4–7)</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/17.6?lang=eng#p6\">D&amp;C 17:6</a>.</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"2\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note2a\" data-full-marker=\"2a\">\n<p data-aid=\"128354561\" id=\"note2a_p1\"><span data-note-category=\"cross-ref\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/27.13-14?lang=eng#p14\">2 Ne. 27:14 (13–14)</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/5.1-16?lang=eng#p15\">D&amp;C 5:15 (1–16)</a>.</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"3\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note3a\" data-full-marker=\"3a\">\n<p data-aid=\"128354563\" id=\"note3a_p1\"><span data-note-category=\"cross-ref\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/11.3?lang=eng#p3\">2 Ne. 11:3</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/27.12-14?lang=eng#p12\">27:12 (12–14)</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/17.3-5?lang=eng#p3\">D&amp;C 17:3 (3–5)</a>.</span></p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"b\" id=\"note3b\" data-full-marker=\"3b\">\n<p data-aid=\"128354565\" id=\"note3b_p1\"><span data-note-category=\"cross-ref\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/5.25?lang=eng#p25\">D&amp;C 5:25</a>.</span></p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"c\" id=\"note3c\" data-full-marker=\"3c\">\n